mkv2mp4
=======
Chad Gioia <cgioia@gmail.com>

Description
-----------
This is a utility to convert Matroska video (MKV) to MP4 (M4V),
ostensibly for viewing on an AppleTV or an Apple iPad, using Handbrake.

The real magic comes in the form of extracting an SSA/ASS subtitle track from the Matroska container, converting it to a format accepted by MP4 (SRT-style subtitles), and muxing it in to the newly converted file.

Prerequisites
-------------
HandbrakeCLI - http://handbrake.fr/
SublerCLI - http://code.google.com/p/subler/
mkvtoolnix - http://www.bunkus.org/videotools/mkvtoolnix/